original_title: The Diana Story: Part III: Legacy of Love
overview: A late night phone call from Paris brought news that would rock the world. The sudden and tragic death of Princess Diana devastated millions. Hear what it was really like to be at the eye of the storm, as Diana's closest friend and confidant shares his story of heartbreak and farewell.
tagline: A late night phone call from Paris brought news that would rock the world.
title: The Diana Story: Part III: Legacy of Love
